        "answer": "由正弦定理及$acosC+\\sqrt{3}asinC-b-c=0$，可得\n\n$\\sin AcosC+\\sqrt{3}\\sin AsinC-\\sin B-\\sin C=0$，\n\n注意到$\\sin B=\\sin(A+C)$，\n\n则$\\sin AcosC+\\sqrt{3}\\sin AsinC-\\sin(A+C)-\\sin C=0$，\n\n于是$\\sin AcosC+\\sqrt{3}\\sin AsinC-(\\sin AcosC+\\cos AsinC)-\\sin C=0$，\n\n整理可得$\\sqrt{3}\\sin AsinC-\\cos AsinC-\\sin C=0$。\n\n即$\\sin C(\\sqrt{3}\\sin A-\\cos A-1)=0$。\n\n因为$C\\in(0,\\pi)$，所以$\\sin C\\neq 0$，\n\n所以$\\sqrt{3}\\sin A-\\cos A=1$，即$2(\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\sin A-\\frac{1}{2}\\cos A)=1$，\n\n于是$\\sin(A-\\frac{\\pi}{6})=\\frac{1}{2}$。\n\n又$A\\in(0,\\pi)$，所以$A-\\frac{\\pi}{6}=\\frac{\\pi}{6}$，即$A=\\frac{\\pi}{3}$。\n\n答案：$\\frac{\\pi}{3}$"
    },
    {
        "id": "722",
        "question": "在锐角三角形ABC中, 角A, B, C的对边分别为a, b, c, $\\frac{b}{a}+\\frac{a}{b}=6\\cos C$, 则$\\frac{\\tan C}{\\tan A}+\\frac{\\tan C}{\\tan B}=$______.",
        "answer": "$\\because \\frac{b}{a}+\\frac{a}{b}=6\\cos C$,\n$\\therefore \\frac{b^{2}+a^{2}}{ab}=6\\cdot \\frac{a^{2}+b^{2}-c^{2}}{2ab}$,\n$\\therefore 2a^{2}+2b^{2}=3c^{2}$.\n\n而$\\frac{\\tan C}{\\tan A}+\\frac{\\\tan C}{\\tan B}=\\frac{\\sin C\\cos A}{\\sin A\\cos C}+\\frac{\\sin C\\cos B}{\\sin B\\cos C}$,\n\n由正弦定理及余弦定理的推论可得\n$\\frac{\\tan C}{\\tan A}+\\frac{\\tan C}{\\tan B}=\\frac{1}{\\cos C}(\\frac{c}{a}\\cdot \\frac{c^{2}+b^{2}-a^{2}}{2bc}+\\frac{c}{b}\\cdot \\frac{a^{2}+c^{2}-b^{2}}{2ac})$\n\n$=\\frac{1}{\\cos C}\\cdot \\frac{2c^{2}}{2ab}$\n\n$=\\frac{2ab}{a^{2}+b^{2}-c^{2}}\\cdot \\frac{2c^{2}}{2ab}$\n\n$=\\frac{2c^{2}}{a^{2}+b^{2}-c^{2}}$\n\n$=4$."
    },
    {
        "id": "723",
        "question": "在△ABC中, 已知(a+b+c)(a+b-c)=3ab, 且2cos Asin B=sin C, 试确定△ABC的形状.",
        "answer": "方法一(利用边的关系来判断)\n由正弦定理得 $\\frac{\\sin C}{\\sin B}=\\frac{c}{b}$, 由2cos Asin B=sin C, 得$\\cos A=\\frac{\\sin C}{2\\sin B}=\\frac{c}{2b}$.\n又$\\cos A=\\frac{b^{2}+c^{2}-a^{2}}{2bc}$, $\\therefore\\frac{c}{2b}=\\frac{b^{2}+c^{2}-a^{2}}{2bc}$, 即$c^{2}=b^{2}+c^{2}-a^{2}$,\n$\\therefore a=b$.\n又(a+b+c)(a+b-c)=3ab,\n$\\therefore(a+b)^{2}-c^{2}=3ab$,\n$\\therefore4b^{2}-c^{2}=3b^{2}$,\n$\\therefore b=c$.\n综上, a=b=c, $\\therefore$ △ABC为等边三角形."
    },
    {
        "id": "724",
        "question": "在△ABC中，A=60°，AC=4，BC=2$\\sqrt{3}$，则△ABC的面积等于______.",
        "answer": "（先求出角度，再利用三角形的面积公式S=$\\frac{1}{2}$absinC求解）\n\n在△ABC中，根据正弦定理，得$\\frac{AC}{\\sin B}=\\frac{BC}{\\sin A}$，\n所以$\\frac{4}{\\sin B}=\\frac{2\\sqrt{3}}{\\sin 60°}$，解得sin B=1.\n因为B∈(0°,120°)，所以B=90°，所以C=30°,\n所以△ABC的面积S_{△ABC}=$\\frac{1}{2}$·AC·BC·sin C=2$\\sqrt{3}$."
    },
    {
        "id": "725",
        "question": "在△ABC中,内角A,B,C所对的边分别是a,b,c,且c=2,C=$\\frac{\\pi}{3}$.\n(1)若△ABC的面积等于$\\sqrt{3}$,求a,b;\n(2)若sin B=2sin A,求△ABC的面积.",
        "answer": "在分析题目的时候要注意三角形面积公式与余弦定理的特点,S=$\\frac{1}{2}$absin C与c^{2}=a^{2}+b^{2}-2abcos C都含有ab,这正是解题的突破口.\n(1)由余弦定理,得a^{2}+b^{2}-ab=4 ①,\n又△ABC的面积等于$\\sqrt{3}$,所以$\\frac{1}{2}$absin C=$\\sqrt{3}$,得ab=4 ②,\n联立①②得方程组$\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}{{a}^{2}+{b}^{2}-ab=4,}\\\\{ab=4,}\\end{array}\\right.$解得$\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}{a=2,}\\\\{b=2.}\\end{array}\\right.$\n\n(2)由正弦定理及sin B=2sin A,得b=2a ③,\n联立①③得方程组$\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}{{a}^{2}+{b}^{2}-ab=4,}\\\\{b=2a,}\\end{array}\\right.$解得$\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}{a=\\frac{2\\sqrt{3}}{3},}\\\\{b=\\frac{4\\sqrt{3}}{3},}\\end{array}\\right.$\n\n所以△ABC的面积S=$\\frac{1}{2}$absin C=$\\frac{2\\sqrt{3}}{3}$."
    }
